location.fullValue: Residence Three Plan, Magnolia at Granite Bay

data.description: Discover an exquisite 3.2-acre estate nestled in the sought-after Carolinda neighborhood of Granite Bay. This exceptional property seamlessly blends elegance with the beauty of nature, offering facilities for horse enthusiasts, separate pastures, and a charming chicken coop. The luxurious resort-style saltwater pool, solar panels ensuring energy independence, and a versatile workshop enhance your quality of life, while a seasonal pond adds to the property's overall charm. A separate entrance provides access to the rear pasture, workshop, and barn. The backyard is secure for dogs with fencing, and the pool is enclosed for safety. Two pastures an upper and a lower are also fenced appropriately for the animals.    The master suite on the first floor exudes sophistication, boasting elevated finishes and a design that reflects luxury throughout. Experience the epitome of upscale living right in the heart of Granite Bay. Don't miss the opportunity to explore 7811 Bartley Ct and uncover a world of opulence and tranquility that awaits you. 2023-11-25
